<item>
            <title>[LU-976] Test failure for mmp on ZFS filesystems</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-976</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/555fe8a0-392d-11e1-b15b-5254004bbbd3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/555fe8a0-392d-11e1-b15b-5254004bbbd3&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ZFS does not support MMP today, so it should be skipped if run for FSTYPE=zfs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Orion patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/1933&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/1933&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Master patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/1934&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/1934&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
